This class contains the profile of the test generation process. The most commonly used parameters in this profile include degree of interaction (DOI), test generation mode (Mode), test generation algorithms (Algorithm), and randomizing don't care values (randstar).

These parameters can be specified in the GUI or on the command line in the following format: -D=. For example, -DDOI=3 specifies that degree of interaction is 3.
